CONTENT NOTICE:
This tool is an interactive wrapper and reference interface built around
content from the following books:

- "Blue Team Field Manual (BTFM)" by Alan White & Ben Clark
- "Red Team Field Manual v2 (RTFM)" by Ben Clark & Nick Downer

All commands, techniques, and reference material are sourced from these
publications and used here for educational purposes only. The original authors
retain all rights to their respective works.

